PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,FA new AI tool that colour-codes
OL,7,Fdifferent parts of the body during
OL,8,Flive operations has been used by
OL,9,Fsurgeons for the first time in the UK.
OL,11,FThe tool highlights different parts of
OL,12,Fthe anatomy in real time on a screen
OL,13,Fand is used alongside robotic or
OL,14,Flaparoscopic surgery. It helps
OL,15,Fsurgeons as they protect or dissect
OL,16,Fparts of the anatomy.
OL,18,FMedics at St Mark's, the National
OL,19,FBowel Hospital, used the tool to
OL,20,Foperate on a patient in her 60s on
OL,21,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,FExperts have said the tool, known as
OL,7,Fthe Eureka system, helps precision,
OL,8,Fefficiency and safety.
OL,10,FThe portable AI unit was developed by
OL,11,Fsurgeons in Japan who trained the tool
OL,12,Fusing thousands of videos of surgical
OL,13,Fprocedures.
OL,15,FThe operation on Thursday marked the
OL,16,Ffirst time it has been used during
OL,17,Fsurgery outside of Japan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,FThe patient, who has not been named,
OL,7,Freceived a bowel resection at the
OL,8,Fhospital, which is part of London
OL,9,FNorth West University Healthcare NHS
OL,10,FTrust.
OL,12,FConsultant surgeon Mr Kapil Sahnan
OL,13,Fdescribed the tool as an "extra
OL,14,Fhelping arm".
OL,16,FHe said that it helps "look at your
OL,17,Flive surgery and start telling you
OL,18,Fwhich are the hidden structures which
OL,19,Fperhaps you can't see".
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@LO]xD@WOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,FHe added: "And the hope and the idea
OL,7,Fbeing is, that if you can identify
OL,8,Fthese, that the operation becomes
OL,9,Fsafer, you have this kind of extra
OL,10,Fhelping arm with artificial
OL,11,Fintelligence running at the same time
OL,12,Fas your surgery, preventing errors and
OL,13,Fmaking everything a lot more safe.
OL,15,F"And we were the first hospital in the
OL,16,Fworld outside of Japan to use it."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
