FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,FHe continued: "Another way of thinking
OL,7,Fabout it is, I remember that my mother
OL,8,Fused to use an A to Z when she had to
OL,9,Fplan routes. Now we all use Google
OL,10,FMaps and Waze.
OL,12,F"And this is that version of kind of
OL,13,Fnavigation that now has been applied
OL,14,Fto surgery.
OL,16,F"The difference has been that real
OL,17,Ftime aspect, so you can see it at the
OL,18,Fsame time as you're operating.
OL,26,@nD@OOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,F"The idea being is you want to prevent
OL,7,Fany errors happening before they do,
OL,8,Fand one way to do that is use, not
OL,9,Fhuman intelligence but intelligence,
OL,10,Fwhich has been derived from thousands
OL,11,Fand thousands and thousands of
OL,12,Foperative videos where people have
OL,13,Fgone through and labelled things.
OL,15,F"So the computer can see things before
OL,16,Fthe human eye can."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,FHe added: "You get these really
OL,7,Fbeautiful images, they put colour
OL,8,Foverlays over the operative images
OL,9,Fwhich can either be on constantly, or
OL,10,Fthey can pulse."
OL,12,FMr Sahnan said work was under way to
OL,13,Fwork out how "we can genuinely prove
OL,14,Fthat this is going to be advantageous
OL,15,Fand, more importantly, how we can
OL,16,Fstart rolling it out.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@PO]uD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780711406
OL,3,CUK first AI driven surgery colour-
OL,4,Ccodes patient anatomy
OL,6,F"We're lucky to have it today, but it
OL,7,Fwould be amazing if everybody had it
OL,8,Fin the next couple of years, it would
OL,9,Fmake surgery for everybody a lot
OL,10,Fsafer."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
